        <sponsor name-id="L000571">Mrs. Lummis</sponsor> (for herself, <cosponsor name-id="W000800">Mr. Welch</cosponsor>, <cosponsor name-id="S000244">Mr. Sensenbrenner</cosponsor>, <cosponsor name-id="P000523">Mr. Price of North Carolina</cosponsor>, <cosponsor name-id="G000535">Mr. Guti√©rrez</cosponsor>, and <cosponsor name-id="J000289">Mr. Jordan</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was referred to the <committee-name committee-id="HBU00">Committee on the Budget</committee-name>
      </action-desc>
